<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-21092] Xml route generated by Camel Jbang does not respect the xsd used</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-21092</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when using Camel JBang init to genrate an xml file, it genrates:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&amp;lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;UTF-8&quot;?&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;camel xmlns=&quot;http://camel.apache.org/schema/spring&quot;
    xmlns:xsi=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance&quot; xsi:schemaLocation=&quot;             http://camel.apache.org/schema/spring             https://camel.apache.org/schema/spring/camel-spring.xsd&quot;&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;route id=&quot;route-06280b52-bf6a-4459-91d1-fa081325d4a2&quot;&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;from uri=&quot;timer:xml?period=1000&quot;/&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;setBody&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;simple&amp;gt;Hello Camel from ${routeId}&amp;lt;/simple&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;/setBody&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;log message=&quot;${body}&quot;/&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/route&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/camel&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;which is giving this xsd validation:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Cvc-elt.1.a: Cannot Find The Declaration Of Element &apos;camel&apos;., Line &apos;2&apos;, Column &apos;199&apos;.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
